features: Pull Back Fighter Toy: No batteries are needed. Simply pull back the fighter jet and release to see it glide swiftly across the floor, a feature that promises to captivate and thrill young minds.
Sound & Light: Adding to the excitement, a gentle press on the jet's head activates flashing lights and realistic sound effects, providing an immersive play experience.

Realistic Details: This pull-back fighter model is designed according to the real fighter, to restore the original appearance of the fighter to the greatest extent, with this fighter model, they can not only see its realistic features but also interact with them. The fighter model achieves this through its well-designed details, which provide a vivid experience to children who want to understand it.

High Quality: Crafted with precision, this toy replicates the intricate details of a real fighter jet, offering both a visual treat and an interactive learning tool. Made from high-quality, non-toxic alloy metal and plastic, it's durable and safe for kids.

Ideal Gift for Kids: This airplane toy, with its authentic design and sensory features, makes an excellent gift for children, and is also a great addition for collectors of military models. Perfect for birthdays, holidays, and special occasions, it's sure to provide endless entertainment and educational value.
